e with an icon. Text between [ ] signs stands for a certain type of icon. </Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SCENE ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TEXT ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZATION NOTES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEV TEAM / MISC NOTES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">OLD TEXT</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SONO_PISTOL</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sono Pistol</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pistolet dźwiękowy</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Relates to Sound, all abilities that have a Sono- are sound abilities.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SONO_SHOTGUN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sono Shotgun</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzelba dźwiękowa</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Relates to Sound, all abilities that have a Sono- are sound abilities.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PERFORATING_CANNON</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Perforating Cannon</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Działo dziurawiące</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Perforating or penetrating weapon</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SONO_FINS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sono Fins</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sonopłetwy</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Fins like a decorative cloak with fin shaped parts</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">REVERB_DAGGER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Reverb Dagger</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sztylet pogłosowy</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">A dagger that creates Reverberations with sound</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LAST_RESORT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Last Resort</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Tylko ty</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">As in the only option available</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LAST_RESORT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">A short range thermal shotgun, for when escape isn't an option</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzelba termiczna krótkiego zasięgu – gdy ucieczka już nie wchodzi w grę.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">A small shotgun that does heat damage</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CARBON_GLAIVE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Carbon Glaive</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Glewia diamentowa</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CARBON_GLAIVE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strike through all enemies in front of this unit and rend their armor</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Razi wszystkich wrogów znajdujących się przed jednostką i przebija ich pancerze.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Rend armor as in to break through it</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALPHA_CLAWS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Alpha Claws</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pazury alfy</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALPHA_CLAWS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Acid coated titanium fighting claws</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Tytanowe pazury bojowe pokryte kwasem.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Fighting claws like a bladed glove</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SONIC_AMPLIFICATION_BATTERY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sonic Amplification Battery</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bateria wzmocnienia dźwiękowego</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Battery as in large weaponry like a cannon</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SONIC_AMPLIFICATION_BATTERY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Unleash sonic waves at the target, damaging it and adjacent targets.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Razi cel falami dźwiękowymi, zadając obrażenia jemu samemu i jednostkom sąsiadującym.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Loud sound waves that hurt units</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GENETIC_DESTABILIZER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Genetic Destabilizer</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Destabilizacja genetyczna</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">As in to weaken and change the shape of a unit genetically</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GENETIC_DESTABILIZER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Biochemical attack that can scramble Biological unit DNA</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Atak biochemiczny, który może uszkodzić DNA jednostek organicznych.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Scrambling unit DNA as in to change the genetics of a living being</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GENETIC_DESTABILIZER_EFFECT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Destabilize</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Destabilizacja</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">As in to weaken and change the shape of</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GENETIC_DESTABILIZER_EFFECT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{BioChance}[strengthbio/] strength chance to apply [abilityred]Destabilize[/abilityred] to Tier 1 and 2 Biological and Cyborg units.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Szansa ({BioChance}[strengthbio/] siły) na spowodowanie [abilityred]destabilizacji[/abilityred] u jednostek organicznych i cyborgów klasy 1 i 2.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">HORROR</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Horror</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Przerażenie</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Horror as in an unspeakable and scary object</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">HORROR</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Launch a Psionic attack that bounces off the target to strike an additional random enemy</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Atak psioniczny, który odbija się od celu i trafia losowo wybranego dodatkowego wroga.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ASSASSINS_FIXATION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Assassin's Fixation</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Mania zabijania</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Fixation as in focusing on a single target</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="90"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ASSASSINS_FIXATION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire at a target; part of the Assassin's Kit[br/][br/]When equipped with [titlebrown]Assassin's Persistence[/titlebrown], hero gains the [abilityBlue]Assassin's Kit[/abilityBlue] buff</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzela do celu. Jest to część zestawu zabójcy.[br/][br/]Po wyposażeniu także w [titlebrown]wytrwałość zabójcy[/titlebrown] bohater uzyskuje premię [abilityBlue]zestawu zabójcy[/abilityBlue].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">VIRAL_SNIPER_RIFLE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Viral Sniper Rifle</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wirusowy karabin snajperski</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Viral as in infectious or contaminated with disease</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">VIRAL_SNIPER_RIFLE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">A multi-purpose Therian sniper rifle</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Uniwersalny karabin snajperski Terian</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ACORN_SUPPORT_POUCH</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Acorn Support Pouch</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sakiewka żołędzi pomocniczych</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Pouch as in container
Acorn, as in the fruit of an oak tree</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ACORN_SUPPORT_POUCH</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Contains Resistance Acorn and Healing Acorn</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zawiera żołądź odporności i żołądź regenerujący</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Acorn, as in the fruit of an oak tree, resistance as in to strengthen defense</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACORN_ASSAULT_POUCH</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Acorn Assault Pouch</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sakiewka żołędzi szturmowych</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Pouch as in container
