r 2 [turn/]</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wysyła dron sonoemisyjny, który zadaje obrażenia pobliskim jednostkom i ulega samozniszczeniu po 2 [turn/].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">SONIC_EMITTER_DRONE_SUMMON</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Damages all units within {range} hexes for {damage} [damagephysical/]</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zadaje {damage} [damagephysical/] pkt. obrażeń wszystkim jednostkom w promieniu {range} pól.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ASSASSINS_PERSISTENCE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Assassin's Persistence</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wytrwałość zabójcy</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">As in the embodiment of persistence in hunting down a target</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="90"><Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ASSASSINS_PERSISTENCE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Close in for the kill; part of the Assassin's Kit[br/][br/]When equipped with [titlebrown]Assassin's Fixation[/titlebrown], hero gains the [abilityBlue]Assassin's Kit[/abilityBlue] buff</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zbliż się, żeby zabić. Jest to część zestawu zabójcy.[br/][br/]Po wyposażeniu także w [titlebrown]manię zabijania[/titlebrown] bohater uzyskuje premię [abilityBlue]zestawu zabójcy[/abilityBlue].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DISORIENTATING_SOUND_EMITTER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Disorientating Sound Emitter</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sonoemiter dezorientujący</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">A device that confuses nearby enemies</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="75"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DISORIENTATING_SOUND_EMITTER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">At end of turn, unit damages adjacent enemy units for {Damage} [damagephysical/] with {StatusChance}[strengthphysical/] strength chance to become [abilityred]Disorientated[/abilityred] for {DebuffDuration}[turn/]</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Na koniec tury jednostka zadaje {Damage} [damagephysical/] pkt. obrażeń sąsiadującym jednostkom wroga z szansą o sile {StatusChance}[strengthphysical/] na spowodowanie [abilityred]dezorientacji[/abilityred] na {DebuffDuration}[turn/].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">V4_AUTO_STIMS_BLIND_RAGE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">V4 Auto Stims: Blind Rage</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Autostymulatory w. 4 – ślepa furia</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Blind Rage as in to make something extremely angry with no accuracy in their actions</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">V4_AUTO_STIMS_BLIND_RAGE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">When health drops to {DamageThreshold}% or lower, unit has -{AccuracyDebuff}% accuracy, but deals {DamageBoost}% damage for {Duration}[turn/]</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gdy wytrzymałość zmaleje do {DamageThreshold}% lub mniej, jednostka ma –{AccuracyDebuff}% do celności, ale zadaje o {DamageBoost}% więcej obrażeń przez {Duration}[turn/].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">V4_AUTO_STIMS_CALMING_STATE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">V4 Auto Stims: Calming State</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Autostymulatory w. 4 – uspokojenie</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Claming State as in to feel relaxed and uncaring</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">V4_AUTO_STIMS_CALMING_STATE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">When health drops to {DamageThreshold}% or lower, unit ignores morale penalties and gains {AccuracyBoost}% accuracy for {Duration}[turn/]</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gdy wytrzymałość zmaleje do {DamageThreshold}% lub mniej, jednostka ignoruje kary do morale i zyskuje {AccuracyBoost}% do celności na {Duration}[turn/].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EMERGENCY_COMBAT_REGENERATOR</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Emergency Combat Regenerator</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ratunkowy regenerator polowy</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EMERGENCY_COMBAT_REGENERATOR</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">When health reaches {threshold}% or lower, unit is healed for {healValue}[hp/]</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gdy wytrzymałość zmaleje do {threshold}% lub mniej, jednostka odzyska {healValue}[hp/].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TRANSFORMATION_HUNTER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DNA Injector: Prowler</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zastrzyk DNA – prześladowca</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">DNA Injector as in a device that changes the DNA of a unit</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TRANSFORMATION_BOUNCER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">