<Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ta jednostka została zdestabilizowana genetycznie i przekształciła się w kolosalną protowiórkę.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">As in a primitive squirrel</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ASSASSINS_PREY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Assassin's Prey</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ofiara zabójcy</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Prey as in the subject of a hunt</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ASSASSINS_PREY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MODIFIER_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{KineticChance}[StrengthPhysical/] strength chance to inflict [abilityred]Impaired[/abilityred] on Heroes or Leaders.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Szansa o sile {KineticChance}[StrengthPhysical/] na spowodowanie [abilityred]osłabienia[/abilityred] u bohaterów lub przywódców.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ASSASSINS_KIT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Assassin's Kit</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zestaw zabójcy</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="90"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ASSASSINS_KIT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Both parts of the Assassin's Kit are equipped, granting each weapon an additional {CriticalBuff}% critical hit chance.[br/]Both weapons now have the [abilityBlue]Assassin's Prey[/abilityblue] effect, granting a chance to inflict [abilityred]Impaired[/abilityred] on Heroes or Leaders.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Postać używa obu części zestawu zabójcy, dzięki czemu każda jej broń zyskuje dodatkowe {CriticalBuff}% do szansy na trafienie krytyczne.[br/]Obie mają też efekt [abilityBlue]ofiary zabójcy[/abilityblue], dający szansę na spowodowanie [abilityred]osłabienia[/abilityred] u bohaterów lub przywódców.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BANNER_OF_THE_UNION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Banner of the Union</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sztandar Związku</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BANNER_OF_THE_UNION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Vanguard and Paragon units in the wielder's stack gain {MoraleBonus} Morale. Vanguard and Paragon units firing on the bearer suffer {AccuracyPenalty} accuracy.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Jednostki Awangardy i Wcielenia w armii właściciela zyskują {MoraleBonus} do morale. Jednostki Awangardy i Wcielenia ostrzeliwujące właściciela doznają kary {AccuracyPenalty} do celności.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BANNER_OF_THE_UNION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">STACK_MODIFIER_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{MoraleBonus}</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{MoraleBonus}</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BANNER_OF_THE_UNION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MODIFIER_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Vanguard and Paragon units firing on the bearer suffer {AccuracyPenalty} accuracy.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Jednostki Awangardy i Wcielenia ostrzeliwujące właściciela doznają kary {AccuracyPenalty} do celności.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">FINISH_THE_JOB</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Finish the Job</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wykończenie</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">FINISH_THE_JOB</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{DamageBoost} damage against targets affected by: [abilityred]Subject of Fixation, Catatonic, Concussed, Crippled or Disabled[/abilityred]</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{DamageBoost} do obrażeń przy atakowaniu celów dotkniętych: [abilityred]manią, katatonią, wstrząsem, okaleczeniem lub unieszkodliwieniem[/abilityred].</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">In the text below, any inserted strings - anything of the form {text} - is replaced by an integer value for the thing described in the brackets. If the {text} is not followed by a unit - e.g. shields, hitpoints - the icon for the unit is inserted together with the integer. The same holds for symbols - e.g. '+', '%' - which are occasionally inserted together with the integer.</Data></Cell></Row></Table><WorksheetOptions xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel"><Unsynced/><Selected/><Panes><Pane><Number>3</Number><ActiveRow>10</ActiveRow><ActiveCol>2</ActiveCol></Pane></Panes><ProtectObjects>False</ProtectObjects><ProtectScenarios>False</ProtectScenarios></WorksheetOptions></Worksheet></Workbook>